title: Textbooks.rar
description:
This is my collection of petroleum engineering textbooks.  I made it all one rar file for simplicity.  I decided to upload them cause they were a bitch to find and I want to help out.

The thermodynamics and organic chemistry books are a few years old, but I guarantee they have 99% the same content as the newest editions.  Both are great books.



Here's all that is is included:



Applied Drilling Engineering (Bourgoyne, Millheim)

Basic Reservoir Simulation (Ertekin)

Elementary Principles Of Chemical Processes (Felder, Rousseau)

Enhanced Oil Recovery (Green, Willhite)

Fundamentals of Reservoir Engineering (L.P. Dake)

Gas Reservoir Engineering (Lee, Wattenbarger)

Organic Chemistry (D. Klein)

Petroleum Engineering Handbook Vol. 1-General

Surface Production Operations, Volume 1, Third Edition (Arnold, Stewart)

Theory, Measurement, and Interpretation of Well Logs (Bassiouni)

Thermodynamics 7E (Cengel)
